import { _ } from '@ag-grid-community/core';
var getFont = function (props) {
    var type = props[0], typeface = props[1], script = props[2], panose = props[3];
    return {
        name: "a:" + type,
        properties: {
            rawMap: {
                script: script,
                typeface: typeface,
                panose: panose
            }
        }
    };
};
